Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:40.84,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}拉下拉鍊後 就能化身成一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:46.81,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}為了尋找重要的事物 也能抵達深海之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:53.63,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}隨著超越深度 也能解開鈕扣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:54.39,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}Lag-Rin Lag-Rin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:58.30,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}馬上就去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:01.55,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}只要當你的緊急信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.09,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}向我發起之際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:06.70,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}圓圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.01,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}轉動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:13.67,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}將命運改寫下一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.61,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}開始飛翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:20.87,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}Fly Away On A Brighter Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:26.90,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}即便有令人咋舌難以邁開步伐的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.32,op-cht,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fade(500,500)}更能熱情如火
